{"tid":183373,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[一個人旅行]去高雄台南台東花蓮 請教巴絲","createTime":"2017-04-02T05:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-02T20:02:13.000Z","uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d200fffd03018bcb192f4e37ea8dedd7814664f1","tid":183373,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:02:00.000Z","msg":"是這樣嘅，<br />\n我打算一個人去高雄 台南 台東 花蓮<br />\n最後返去高雄走<br />\n因為台東同花蓮交通都唔太方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我唔會自駕遊果啲 有咩事都搭火車/的士<br />\n有無巴絲試過咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f9e9cfefdb51e3005e7c13c51535d3d773d4d1","tid":183373,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:25:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"7a17bc9c0b5f8b578befb1350e1238eb9b8b79d2","tid":183373,"uid":94176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:46:45.000Z","msg":"花蓮、台東(更甚!)交通好唔方便，公車班次勁疏，9pm就無。<br />\n的士都好難截，如果想跑多d景點就要預多d錢包車/拼車，一般可以向hotel/ hostel查詢預約包車/拼車。<br />\n<br />\np.s.台東住宿一定要揀近市中心(近夜市/鐵花村個邊)，唔好揀住近台東火車站，我上次去被fake，以為近火車站就繁華d，點知去到發現人跡罕至<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又偏僻又冇嘢食"},{"pid":"dd9dfba81077bbb0d241eee6e8fa210d65c45d46","tid":183373,"uid":23758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T05:51:12.000Z","msg":"去幾耐<br />\n時間唔夠就唔好去d唔多方便既地方"},{"pid":"9442211e68f4dd6b4350912cdb4357f856257d1a","tid":183373,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>花蓮、台東(更甚!)交通好唔方便，公車班次勁疏，9pm就無。<br />\n的士都好難截，如果想跑多d景點就要預多d錢包車/拼車，一般可以向hotel/ hostel查詢預約包車/拼車。<br />\n<br />\np.s.台東住宿一定要揀近市中心(近夜市/鐵花村個邊)，唔好揀住近台東火車站，我上次去被fake，以為近火車站就繁華d，點知去到發現人跡罕至<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又偏僻又冇嘢食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你上次去咗幾多日？<br />\n原來台東咁唔方便 但我今次應該會集中響台東 想去合歡山行山睇花 去池上買米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87483a4de9e0fe44aa83c1a7882e7924d0c0a9f4","tid":183373,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:15:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去幾耐<br />\n時間唔夠就唔好去d唔多方便既地方</blockquote><br />\n我四月尾去 去十日呀<br />\n第一次一條友去咁遠 仲要去山卡啦 有啲驚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bdb8c34980f239cdc6dffe38804b6eb0b194347","tid":183373,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:17:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>花蓮、台東(更甚!)交通好唔方便，公車班次勁疏，9pm就無。<br />\n的士都好難截，如果想跑多d景點就要預多d錢包車/拼車，一般可以向hotel/ hostel查詢預約包車/拼車。<br />\n<br />\np.s.台東住宿一定要揀近市中心(近夜市/鐵花村個邊)，唔好揀住近台東火車站，我上次去被fake，以為近火車站就繁華d，點知去到發現人跡罕至<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又偏僻又冇嘢食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你上次去咗幾多日？<br />\n原來台東咁唔方便 但我今次應該會集中響台東 想去合歡山行山睇花 去池上買米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n合歡山唔係台東喎<br />\n池上米週圍超級市場都有抽啦"},{"pid":"da8b2e170c88850cbd5b7e08bd38fe1b0dc863cc","tid":183373,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:18:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><b