e":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:20:54.000Z","msg":"我想去池上睇吓稻田 同埋想去埋關山鹿野行個轉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b2f79a3fc5cf32cd6cb974bb706b75cb66728e1","tid":183373,"uid":3628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:21:33.000Z","msg":"我5月都去<br />\n預花蓮全程搭的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b61a358e33a4e2efdef922696d59524b04a2a6c3","tid":183373,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呀我講錯 應該係花蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我睇書睇過 合歡山好似南投花蓮交界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去合歡山多數由清境嗰邊上，由花蓮去交通唔方便"},{"pid":"69cc8f3f609be58dc0881bddfdc168f726931ead","tid":183373,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:24:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我5月都去<br />\n預花蓮全程搭的士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打自己去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n阿媽宜家知我自己嘈到拆天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話花蓮僻到仆街 利申 佢上次去家姐男友揸車我無去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29155f315f4772899d30cc2816c1bc77f8d8769c","tid":183373,"uid":70876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:24:48.000Z","msg":"台東你慢慢hea幾日可以搭巴士號"},{"pid":"56952b1c3ae45781b2e5bb353811f9a878d19fff","tid":183373,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呀我講錯 應該係花蓮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我睇書睇過 合歡山好似南投花蓮交界<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去合歡山多數由清境嗰邊上，由花蓮去交通唔方便</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺 好似台中上去方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能去唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a85db983b5cb94d3c5117e7b3453d2c3345076","tid":183373,"uid":94176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>花蓮、台東(更甚!)交通好唔方便，公車班次勁疏，9pm就無。<br />\n的士都好難截，如果想跑多d景點就要預多d錢包車/拼車，一般可以向hotel/ hostel查詢預約包車/拼車。<br />\n<br />\np.s.台東住宿一定要揀近市中心(近夜市/鐵花村個邊)，唔好揀住近台東火車站，我上次去被fake，以為近火車站就繁華d，點知去到發現人跡罕至<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又偏僻又冇嘢食</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝絲打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你上次去咗幾多日？<br />\n原來台東咁唔方便 但我今次應該會集中響台東 想去合歡山行山睇花 去池上買米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n合歡山多數係歸落台中行程，d人上完清境會順便上合歡山武嶺睇日出<br />\n<br />\n我都係獨遊，12月尾個陣去咗12日台灣<br />\n高雄--&gt;台東--&gt;花蓮--&gt;宜蘭--&gt;台北<br />\n台東同花蓮都係stay咗3日2夜，<br />\n但事後覺得花蓮玩2日1夜都夠，<br />\n反而台東可以預3-4日，因為d景點距離相隔好遠，ideal嘅話可以一日行山線，一日行海線，一日玩台東市區"},{"pid":"5c0385a67955ba636d021841ed70e2b834dc33eb","tid":183373,"uid":94176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-02T06:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>花蓮、台東(更甚!)交通好唔方便，公車班次勁疏，9pm就無。<br />\n的士都好難截，如果想跑多d景點就要預多d錢包車/拼車，一般可以向hotel/ hostel查詢預約包車/拼車。<br />\n<br />\np.s.台東住宿一定要揀近市中心(近夜市/鐵花村個邊)，唔好揀住近台東火車站，我上次去被fake，以為近火車站就繁華d，點知去到發現人跡罕至<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又偏僻又冇嘢食</b